author: Corridor Crew
description: Have you ever heard about Astartes and Sayama Pedersen? Well, if you have, you probably also know about the Warhammer episode from Secret Level, and how amazing it look. This is because the very same Sayama Pedersen got to work as a Layout director in it. Tim Miller explains how this happened, and what Layout means.
title: This FAN got to work on THE REAL THING
